content: Very sad to report that legendary NY rapper Prodigy from #MobbDeep has passed away at the age of 42. He fought a life long battle with sickle cell anemia. He was always a big supporter of mine & our community efforts like #push4peace & always showed up for an event or #streetsoldiers show when I asked. Supported me from Day 1.  We had a great talk as always after he did my show for the last time in November 2016. We will miss his big live for helping people. Rest In Paradise, Prodigy. 💕💞💝

#RIP Prodigy of Mobb Deep This ground-breaking influential Hip Hop artist was just 42 years old when he lost his life long battle with sickle cell anemia. He was a friend and supporter of my shows & community events, & in contast to his bold rapper persona, had a quiet warmth & love for people that was genuine. He has millions of fans around the world & was always trying to help others. #RestInParadise  Prodigy
